summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Water Department; accepting a franchise from the Washington State Highway Commission (Franchise No. 5340) for the installation, operation and maintenance of a twelve-inch City watermain in State Route 900 (Empire Way South) between the south corporate limits of the City and 107th Street and in a small portion of said 107th Street easterly from Empire Way South and authorizing execution and delivery of an "acceptance of franchise" therefor.
